SetUp Java and Android Path
1. Goto Manage Jenkins ->
Global Tool Configration
2. Setup Java Path in Env,
JAVA Default Location = /us/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64/
3. Click Save and Apply and Back button
4. Click on Configration - in Env. Set the Android_SDK path
ANDROID_HOME = /us/lib/android-sdk/
Setup Path in Jenkins
JAVA Default Location = /us/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-and64/
3. Click Save and Apply and Back button
4. Click on Configration - in Env. Set the Android_SDK path
